《'''決勝時空戰區'''》（{{lang-en|''Masters of the Universe''}}）是一部1987年美國[[科幻片|科幻]][[動作片|動作片]]，由[[蓋瑞·葛達|蓋瑞·葛達]]執導，改編自[[美泰兒公司|美泰兒公司]]旗下的玩具《[[太空超人|太空超人]]》。電影主演包括[[杜夫·朗格|杜夫·朗格]]、[[法蘭克·藍吉拉|法蘭克·藍吉拉]]、[[柯特妮·考克斯|柯特妮·考克斯]]、[[詹姆士·托根|詹姆士·托根]]、[[克里斯汀娜·皮克勒斯|克里斯汀娜·皮克勒斯]]和[[梅格·福斯特|梅格·福斯特]]主演。《決勝時空戰區》於1987年8月7日在美國廣泛上映。電影獲得了普遍負評和失敗的票房，但在之後成為了[[邪典電影|邪典電影]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/he-man-masters-of-the-universe-christopher-yost-writer-1201573946/|title='Thor: Ragnarok' Scribe to Pen 'Masters of the Universe' for Sony (EXCLUSIVE)|last=Kroll|first=Justin|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2015-08-19|accessdate=2016-04-01|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305062235/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/he-man-masters-of-the-universe-christopher-yost-writer-1201573946/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==劇情==
故事敘述主角太空超人和邪惡的幽靈王為了搶奪一把能操縱時間與空間的時空鑰匙，雙方就此展開天人交戰。

==重啟版==
2007年，傳出[[吳宇森|吳宇森]]將擔任重啟版的《太空超人》電影；儘管網路上有著關於製作和選角的傳言，但該計畫仍未正式啟動，據傳電影的版權已被美泰兒公司收回<ref>Clint Morris, [http://www.moviehole.net/news/20061130_fox2000_no_longer_has_the_powe.html Fox2000 no longer has the Power of Grayskull] {{Wayback|url=http://www.moviehole.net/news/20061130_fox2000_no_longer_has_the_powe.html |date=20080511162413 }}, ''Moviehole'', November 30, 2006.</ref>。

2009年9月，[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影業]]接管了[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟公司]]的真人改編權，而監製[[喬·西佛|喬·西佛]]則因創作方向不一而退出<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118009027.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564 |title=Barbie's a living doll at Universal – Entertainment News, Film News, Media |publisher=Variety |date=2009-09-23 |accessdate=2010-04-28 |archive-date=2010-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100907063712/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118009027.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。索尼與[[Escape_Artists|Escape Artists]]的陶德·布萊克、傑森·布盧門撒爾、[[史蒂夫·提許|史蒂夫·提許]]開始隨著[[哥倫比亞影業|哥倫比亞影業]]發展該電影。2010年4月，索尼聘請了編劇邁克·芬奇和亞里士·李維克編寫一份新劇本<ref name="drees">{{cite web |last=drees |first=Rich |url=http://www.filmbuffonline.com/FBOLNewsreel/wordpress/2010/04/12/masters-of-the-universe-gets-screenwriters/ |title=MASTERS OF THE UNIVERSE Gets Screenwriters |publisher=filmbuffonline.com |date= |accessdate=2010-04-12 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019204208/http://www.filmbuffonline.com/FBOLNewsreel/wordpress/2010/04/12/masters-of-the-universe-gets-screenwriters/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來，華納兄弟打算讓《[[功夫熊貓|功夫熊貓]]》的導演[[約翰·史蒂文森_(導演)|約翰·史蒂文森]]來執導。2009年5月12日，宣布劇本改由[[伊凡·多爾帝|伊凡·多爾帝]]負責，史蒂文森仍為導演人選<ref>{{cite web |last=Kit |first=Borys |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3if21dd856cfb9103e7d3bd0bb5a8352f8 |title='Grayskull' lands new writer |publisher=Hollywoodreporter.com |date= |accessdate=2009-05-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090516154418/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3if21dd856cfb9103e7d3bd0bb5a8352f8 |archivedate=2009年5月16日 }}</ref>。

2012年末，[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]報導，[[朱浩偉|朱浩偉]]正在洽談擔任導演<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming|first=Mike |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/07/jon-m-chu-in-masters-of-theuniverse-talks/ |title=Jon M. Chu In ‘Masters Of The Universe’ Talks |publisher=Deadline Hollywood |date= |accessdate=2012-07-30}}</ref>。原太空超人演員[[杜夫·朗格林|杜夫·朗格林]]在接受[[IGN|IGN]]採訪時，透露有望飾演[[藍道國王|藍道國王]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Fleming |first=Mike |url=http://www.ign.com/videos/2012/08/03/dolph-lundgren-on-he-man-reboot |title=He-Man and the Masters of the Universe – Lundgren on He-Man Reboot |publisher=IGN |date= |accessdate=2012-08-03 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307215605/https://www.ign.com/videos/2012/08/03/dolph-lundgren-on-he-man-reboot |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年10月12日，李察·溫克被聘來改寫劇本<ref>{{cite web |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118060695 |title=Wenk to pen 'Masters of the Universe' |publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2012-10-12 |accessdate=2012-10-12 |archive-date=2013-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103140301/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118060695/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月28日，朱浩偉說電影還在測試階段，也不會是裝模作樣的而是個起源故事<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ign.com/videos/2013/03/27/he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe-jon-m-chu-update |title=G.I. Joe: Retaliation Director Talks He-Man Movie |access-date=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308204621/https://www.ign.com/videos/2013/03/27/he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe-jon-m-chu-update |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.toplessrobot.com/2013/03/john_m_chu_gi_joe_masters_of_the_universe_he-man_g.php?page=2 |title=TR Interview: Jon M. Chu Talks G.I. Joe: Retaliation...And Masters Of The Universe! |access-date=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2015-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928003449/http://www.toplessrobot.com/2013/03/john_m_chu_gi_joe_masters_of_the_universe_he-man_g.php?page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 10月7日，據《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》，[[泰瑞·羅西奧|泰瑞·羅西奧]]將撰寫劇本，而陶德·布萊克、傑森·布盧門撒爾、史蒂夫·提許將會擔任監製，且電影將在[[伊特魯里亞|伊特魯里亞]]拍攝；此外，朱浩偉將不會執導<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lone-ranger-writer-tapped-write-644438 |title='Lone Ranger' Co-Writer Tapped to Write 'Masters of the Universe' (Exclusive) |access-date=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308115756/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lone-ranger-writer-tapped-write-644438 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年1月10日，Schmoes Know報導，《[[異星大作戰|異星大作戰]]》的導演[[喬·柯尼許|喬·柯尼許]]、《[[迴路殺手|迴路殺手]]》的導演[[萊恩·詹森|萊恩·詹森]]、《[[母侵|母侵]]》的導演[[安迪·馬希提|安迪·馬希提]]、《[[古魯家族|古魯家族]]》的雙導演[[柯克·狄麥可|柯克·狄麥可]]與[[克里斯·桑德斯|克里斯·桑德斯]]、《[[樂高玩電影|樂高玩電影]]》的雙導演[[菲爾·洛德與克里斯多福·米勒|菲爾·洛德與克里斯多福·米勒]]都是導演候選人<ref>{{cite news |author=The Phantom |url=http://schmoesknow.com/from-the-phantoms-desk-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe-close-to-happening-looking-at-new-directors/ |title=He-Man and the Masters of the Universe Close to Happening; Looking at New Directors! |publisher=Schmoes Know |date=2014-01-10 |accessdate=2014-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113124339/http://schmoesknow.com/from-the-phantoms-desk-he-man-and-the-masters-of-the-universe-close-to-happening-looking-at-new-directors/ |archive-date=2016-01-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2月26日，據報導，[[麥可·凱西爾|麥可·凱西爾]]、[[傑夫·瓦德洛|傑夫·瓦德洛]]、[[哈洛德·茲瓦特|哈洛德·茲瓦特]]和[[克里斯·麥凱|克里斯·麥凱]]是目前的導演候選名單<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/krolljvar/statuses/438809817411354624?screen_name=krolljvar |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308014625/https://twitter.com/krolljvar/statuses/438809817411354624?screen_name=krolljvar |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thewrap.com/man-film-masters-universe-eyes-karate-kid-director-lego-movie-editor-exclusive/ |title=He-Man Film ‘Masters of the Universe’ Director Short-List Includes ‘Lego Movie’ Editor (Exclusive) |accessdate=2014-02-26 |publisher=The Wrap |date=2014-02-26 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308143703/https://www.thewrap.com/man-film-masters-universe-eyes-karate-kid-director-lego-movie-editor-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月9日，Schmoes Know報導，瓦德羅將執導本片，但《好萊塢報導》則稱瓦德羅只是改寫劇本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://schmoesknow.com/a-phantom-exclusive-jeff-wadlow-will-direct-masters-of-the-universe/|title=A PHANTOM EXCLUSIVE: Jeff Wadlow Will Direct MASTERS OF THE UNIVERSE!|publisher=Schmoes Know|date=2014-04-09|accessdate=2014-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107054855/http://schmoesknow.com/a-phantom-exclusive-jeff-wadlow-will-direct-masters-of-the-universe/|archive-date=2016-01-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jeff-wadlow-write-masters-universe-695124|title=Jeff Wadlow to Rewrite 'Masters of the Universe'|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-04-10|accessdate=2014-04-10}}</ref>。

2015年8月19日，[[克里斯多夫·約斯特|克里斯多夫·約斯特]]曾被聘請為電影編劇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://spinoff.comicbookresources.com/2015/08/19/christopher-yost-to-write-masters-of-the-universe-film/|title=Christopher Yost to Write ‘Masters of the Universe’ Film|publisher=Comicbookresources.com|date=2015-08-19|accessdate=2015-08-19|archive-date=2016-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317101922/http://spinoff.comicbookresources.com/2015/08/19/christopher-yost-to-write-masters-of-the-universe-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年1月22日，根據Deadline.com報導，[[喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾|喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾]]將執導本片，邁克·芬奇和亞里士·李維克被找回為電影編劇，而陶德·布萊克、傑森·布盧門撒爾、史蒂夫·提許也將參與監製<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/masters-of-the-universe-mcg-sony-pictures-1201688130/|title=McG Orbiting ‘Masters Of The Universe’ At Sony|publisher=Deadline|last=Fleming, Jr|first=Mike|date=2016-01-22|access-date=2016-06-27|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125123049/https://deadline.com/2016/01/masters-of-the-universe-mcg-sony-pictures-1201688130/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年6月24日，[[凱蘭·魯茲|凱蘭·魯茲]]有望擔任主演<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/kellanlutz/status/746419550699163648 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308041052/https://twitter.com/kellanlutz/status/746419550699163648 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://comicbook.com/2016/06/25/kellan-lutz-met-with-mcg-about-masters-of-the-universe-movie/|title=Kellan Lutz Met With McG About Masters Of The Universe Movie|publisher=ComicBook.com|last=Burlingame|first=Russ|date=2016-06-24|accessdate=2016-06-27|archive-date=2016-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627005021/http://comicbook.com/2016/06/25/kellan-lutz-met-with-mcg-about-masters-of-the-universe-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年4月26日，索尼證實，重啟電影將於2019年12月18日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/842157-masters-of-the-universe-movie|title=By the Power of Grayskull! Masters of the Universe Movie Sets 2019 Release|publisher=Coming Soon|last=Lesnick|first=Silas|date=2017-04-26|accessdate=2017-04-27|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519201226/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/842157-masters-of-the-universe-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>；但喬瑟夫·麥克吉帝·尼克爾已退出導演一職，而劇本則由[[大衛·S·高耶|大衛·S·高耶]]負責<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.avclub.com/masters-of-the-universe-gets-a-release-date-but-loses-1798261157|title=Masters Of The Universe gets a release date, but loses its director|first=Danette|last=Chavez|publisher=''[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]''|date=2017-04-27|access-date=2018-02-10|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309055120/https://news.avclub.com/masters-of-the-universe-gets-a-release-date-but-loses-1798261157|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年12月，據報導，高耶有望執導電影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/david-s-goyer-he-man-masters-of-the-universe/|title=David S. Goyer in Talks to Direct He-Man Film ‘Masters of the Universe’ for Sony (Exclusive)|publisher=Thge Wrap|last=Gonzalez|first=Umberto|date=2017-12-01|access-date=2018-02-10|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225200333/https://www.thewrap.com/david-s-goyer-he-man-masters-of-the-universe/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://omegaunderground.com/2018/01/21/goyer-teases-masters-universe-pre-production-teela-confirmed/|title=Goyer Teases ‘Masters of The Universe’ Is In Pre-Production – Teela Confirmed|publisher=Omega Underground|last=Marc|first=Christopher|date=2018-01-21|access-date=2018-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209063852/https://omegaunderground.com/2018/01/21/goyer-teases-masters-universe-pre-production-teela-confirmed/|archive-date=2018-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2018年2月，高耶將不會執導電影，但仍會擔任編劇和執行製片人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/masters-of-the-universe-he-man-david-goyer-wont-direct-1202692790/|title=‘Masters of the Universe’ Still Needs Director as David S. Goyer Passes (EXCLUSIVE)|publisher=Variety|last=Lang|first=Brent|date=2018-02-08|accessdate=2018-02-08|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308124107/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/masters-of-the-universe-he-man-david-goyer-wont-direct-1202692790/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年4月19日，據報導，《{{le|劫匪幫|Band of Robbers}}》（2015年）的搭檔導演{{le|尼兄弟|Nee Brothers}}被聘來執導電影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/masters-of-the-universe-directors-nee-brothers/|title=‘Masters of the Universe’ Finds New Directors in the Nee Brothers|last=Hall|first=Jacob|work=Slash Film|date=2018-04-19|accessdate=2018-04-20|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119053002/https://www.slashfilm.com/masters-of-the-universe-directors-nee-brothers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年初，宣布[[諾亞·森迪尼奧|諾亞·森迪尼奧]]扮演主角太空超人，預計暑期開拍，最終受到[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影響，該項目不了了之。2021年4月30日，森迪尼奧透過經紀人對外證實，退出本片。

